sellerCard.oneLiner: Welcome to Expert Profile Here Turning Your Ideas into Reality!
sellerCard.description: Greetings. I'm a skilled full stack developer passionate about translating ideas into compelling digital experiences. With over 4 years of practical experience, I've honed my abilities to provide exceptional Web and Mobile application solutions that suit your requirements. My Expertise are includes- PHP, HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript, flutter, Dart, etc. Are you eager to enhance your startup or existing business? Drop me a message anytime! Reach out, and let's discuss how we can improve your online presence together.

description.content:
Are you a startup looking for a front end developer to complete a functional Reactjs App with HTML CSS, Bootstrap, and more? 


Let's get your job done in high quality!


I'm a front end web developer with 5+ years of extensive experience developing mid- to large-scale websites and web applications using HTML, CSS, Bootstrap GSAP, React JS, and jQuery. I will convert any design to a web application as per your requirement, which will be completely mobile-friendly and functional.


I always maintain a long-term relationship with my clients. I can take over the project if you want to build a web app from scratch or maintain existing apps.


Services I Provide:


  • Fully Responsive Functional Web Application
  • Customized Website Designed as Your Desire
  • Front-end Work with REACT/NEXT
  • Pixel Perfect Conversion
  • PSD to HTML, CSS, Reactjs with GSAP, Bootstrap
  • Custom Development
  • CSS Animation Creation
  • Clean Code
  • Fully Responsive
  • E-commerce Functionality
  • API Integration


Technologies I Used:


  • React js
  • Html 5
  • CSS 3
  • jQuery
  • Bootstrap
  • Figma
  • PSD


My promises are:


- Good quality work

- Problem-solving

- Logical mindset

- Time-management

- Team Player

- Good communication


Book a free consultation by cont

questionsAndAnswers.question: What do you need to start working?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I need a doc including complete project details to start the project.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will all pages be responsive and mobile-friendly?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, All the pages are super mobile-friendly and support all devices and browsers.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you customize or redesign an existing website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I will redesign, customize, or fix errors in an existing website also according to your requirements.

reviews.comment: Sanjid and his team are the best web developers I have ever worked with. When I say best I mean it because they’re very professional and caring for you or your project. They’re very knowledgeable and responsive. They deliver on time with no issues and I have had lots of issues but they resolved each and every issues I had and beyond. Whatever modifications I needed for the website they did it even though we hadn’t agreed upon when I hired them. I’m beyond satisfied with their professionalism and I absolutely recommend everyone to hire them without any doubt. They will take care of you 10000% you never imagined before. Thank you guys. I am delighted by your work ethic. Bravooo

Was able to raise $2M dollars for my start up in 30 days with the work Mohammad and his team did!  Fast, responsive and incredibly professional.  Mohammad would always be fast to respond or immediately get on a zoom call to ask questions about my project to make sure it was incredible!

seller_response.comment: Thank you for trusting me with your project. Your professionalism made this experience seamless.

reviews.comment: I spent several days trying to set up the notification on my contact form to get the information I wanted. He was able to complete it quickly and even helped me with a few other minor issues that I hadn’t initially asked about. I highly recommend him!

seller_response.comment: Thank you for your valuable feedback. It was a pleasure to work with you.

reviews.comment: Working with him has been an amassing experience, the website design is beyond my expectations. The quality of the communication and guidance was exceptional and I have recommended him already to many of my network. Thank you very much for the work Ketan and I look forward to working with you on the next phase of the website.

Working with Mohammad Sanjid was a fantastic experience. His professionalism, clear communication, and proactive approach made developing my website seamless, and his thoughtful planning, including storyboard UI discussions, ensured we were always on the same page. Every change I requested was handled quickly and efficiently, resulting in a website that exceeded my expectations.
